      },
      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Once the agents are working in production, the next question is simple.\n- How do we make them better at the job?\n- How do we run them more efficiently as volume grows?",
      "demo_actions": "Open the post-deployment optimization area in Foundry or A365. Frame the goal as quality plus cost.",
      "screenshot": ""
    },
    {
