        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- Start with quality.\n- Foundry rubric evaluators let us score the agent on the work that actually matters in invoice assurance.\n- Use traces from real runs to shape what good looks like.",
      "demo_actions": "Open Foundry rubric evaluators. Show trace-based rubric generation or the evaluator setup flow.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_143122_vlcsnap-2026-06-22-14h31m17s909.png"
    },
