        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "- With that feedback in place, Agent Optimizer can improve the invoice-review agent.\n- The important point is that we are tuning against the real job.\n- The agent gets better at making evidence-backed recommendations in the Waypoint context.",
      "demo_actions": "Open Foundry Agent Optimizer. Show optimization inputs, target rubrics, and an updated result or comparison.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_213153_963_26.jpg"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
