        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "- Quality is only half the story.\n- In production, cost matters too.\n- That is especially true if many invoice reviews are running every day across many suppliers and manufacturing programs.",
      "demo_actions": "Move to the A365 cost view or cost monitoring surface. Show model or run cost metrics.",
