        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "- This is where hill climbing comes in.\n- Take what we learned from the stronger model.\n- Use it to move toward a smaller model that can carry more of the workload at a lower operating cost.",
      "demo_actions": "Show the hill-climbing setup or model comparison from larger model to smaller model.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_213254_487_30.jpg"
    },
