        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "- RLE helps the smaller model close the gap.\n- The goal is not to make every model identical.\n- The goal is to preserve the reasoning quality that matters for invoice review while reducing the cost per run.",
      "demo_actions": "Show the RLE step, training or adaptation signals, and a before-and-after quality comparison.",
